Description:
This is the altar where the sacred flame aspect of the Great Bird is revered. It is here that the natives of Aquarfall celebrate the purifying properties of fire and how, through it, the Great Bird protects its followers while punishing their enemies.

In the center, there is a golden statue of the Great Bird, placed within an ever-burning bowl and surrounded by a lot of ashes. Engraved on the altar is a message stating that those who show their devotion to the Great Bird shall not fear the flames. You wonder if the ashes belong to non-true believers...

The altar is guarded, and in order to continue, you must show your respect to the Great Bird’s sacred flame aspect.
